      <div class="msgContentFrame">Best way to deal with fatigue is to do other things or if you hit fatigue around when you planed to get some sleep, log off and get some rest. I will note that fatigue does not carry over to other deciple of land classes. Each of them has their own fatigue, if one hit's it, then it won't affect the rest. <br /> <br />Usually what I do is save up local leves for when fatigue settles in on all three deciples of land, the poke a little at crafting every now and then.</div>
