      <div class="msgContentFrame">Your assumptions that the damage is coming from mindless targeting/swings, poor gear, or harvesting beyond my level are all incorrect. My point is, plain and simple, post update, I am damaging considerably more logs than before. Most of this happens with the message 'you are getting closer to the mark', which, in turn, I adjust the target marginally one way or the other, and voila, damage. If you don't make this minor targeting adjustment, it will result in a harvesting failure. If I'm missing something here, kindly advise, but I'm firmly convinced some level of ninja nerfing. Regards.</div>
